com.esri.mo2.file.shp
Interface MultiPartShapeZ

All Superinterfaces:
Cloneable, MultiPartShape, MultiPartShapeM
All Known Implementing Classes:
MultiPatchShp, PolygonZShp, PolylineZShp
public interface MultiPartShapeZ
extends MultiPartShapeM

This class declares the methods that are common to all multipart shapes with Z values. The starting index for both points and parts is 0.
